Write test cases for the functions in message.go.  The hello.msg file
is a test message file that contains an arbitrary multihash followed
by a newline, followed by the string "hello world".  The test cases
should include a test for the ParseMessage function.  The ParseMessage
function should be able to parse the multihash and the string from an
io.Reader.  

